  "translations": {
    "en": "As for your child's right, know he is from you and attributed to you in this world's affairs with his good and evil. You are responsible for his good upbringing, guiding him to his Lord, and helping him obey. Act as one who knows he will be rewarded for good and punished for ill. As for your brother's right, know he is your hand, honour, and strength. Do not use him as a weapon for disobedience or equipment for wronging Allah's creatures. Do not abandon helping him. If he obeys Allah, good; otherwise, let Allah be more honoured. There is no strength save in Allah.",
